{"tid":1616156,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩大家提高警覺","createTime":"2019-10-03T10:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T12:52:58.000Z","uid":35125,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f426825352122dd116df6a2dae0fc3313e1ce772","tid":1616156,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:01:29.000Z","msg":"聽聞近排好多人被爆門 想係到再提提大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1）唔好係公開地方（車、餐廳 etc)講發夢既野 細聲都唔得<br />\n2）唔好再帶無謂野出去 重要野如手機ID 放腰包<br />\n3）遮哂個樣同頭髮 唔係帶個口罩就算<br />\n4）小心留意有冇人跟<br />\n5） 得既話 最好換哂成set 衫 （tshirt，褲，拖鞋）<br />\n6)  確保無cam/人睇到先換衫 如果廁所門口有cam都唔得<br />\n因為track到你出入 <br />\n<strong>最住換裝模式為：</strong><br />\n街坊裝出門&mdash;&gt; A點換衫 &mdash;-&gt; 現場 &mdash;-&gt; B點換返街坊裝 &mdash;-&gt; 返屋企<br />\n而A同B附近範圍都唔應該有任何cam,包括商鋪外cctv,天眼,車cam等<br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多 歡迎補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27935f3567fd640f8ea5412acb017e2989987cfb","tid":1616156,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:02:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80db0f0a5cb67bb185b25aaa21beb58d9eaa527c","tid":1616156,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7df73f467d50c1f51e6d27bd705457f306862b","tid":1616156,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:02:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e84448c032ae195f81014ba51310c510cd245d9","tid":1616156,"uid":48942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:03:30.000Z","msg":"雖然有啲麻煩，但保障自己都要做"},{"pid":"b3e9210d5db08e04e53fd673e39d394409be05ec","tid":1616156,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:11:35.000Z","msg":"7）背包一係全黑,係現場就戴raincover<br />\n8）如果冇信心安全歸家 就係信任既地方過一晚夜<br />\n就算你換哂衫 狗都可能睇某時段(如深夜）既cctv 從而縮窄/推斷你有冇份參與"},{"pid":"648296c9f93ce3a6100cf1d3ce768efd47f3dec2","tid":1616156,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:20:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e19d08791a7a87bf849a69cc4f6aaa0e691470f8","tid":1616156,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a49addc7a6fe91b6f42899ff3dd1ae72d3cb54","tid":1616156,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"大家小心d呀"},{"pid":"47b6ba1ab854890d198f3bc86a565f8b752bdb12","tid":1616156,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:56:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8590d2a844f24609c65dc91a822a185c3fad5edd","tid":1616156,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T03:07:30.000Z","msg":"冇人推實用文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131c67b88b91d3611c703d898c825cee6b44ea94","tid":1616156,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:40:49.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"1006314f0e6dcba5cc3f3ab1343c193548fea85f","tid":1616156,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:52:58.000Z","msg":"唉"}]}